Mera app idea yeh hai ki small businesses ko aksar yeh samajh nahi hota ki apne ads aur promotions kaise kiye jaayen. Mera idea yeh hai ki user mere platform par aaye, mujhe apne ad accounts ka detailed data de, aur apne products aur business ke baare mein bataye ki kya hai aur kaise kaam karta hai. Phir mera LLM bot deep research karke uska competitor analysis dega aur ek full strategy build karke dega ki uske product ke ads kaise run hone chahiye. Agar user chahe, to woh mujhe apne ad accounts ka data de sakta hai, aur main uski behalf par MCP/API calls karke strategy ke hisaab se ads setup kar dunga. Main Google ke Pomelli ka use karke uske liye creatives aur LLM bhi bana dunga, aur uske campaigns ko bhi optimize karunga. Ab jaise DV360 hai, usme kuch API calls nahi ki ja sakti hain aur user ko UI se hi kaam karna padta hai, to main kya soch raha hoon ki koi ek browser agent leke main woh saare kaam bhi kar doon jo API se possible nahi hain.